I think you all know him, but let me explain to beginners who don't know him.

77
00:02:44,420 --> 00:02:45,960
His real name is Neruo Higurashi.

78
00:02:46,420 --> 00:02:49,060
He works in the same police station as us, Kameari Park.

79
00:02:52,000 --> 00:02:55,200
He has superpowers such as awareness, drive and fire.

80
