But he uses superpowers to use his body.

82
00:03:03,060 --> 00:03:04,060
He consumes his body excessively.

83
00:03:05,040 --> 00:03:10,140
That's why he sleeps 20, 50 hours more and more.

84
00:03:10,140 --> 00:03:11,560
Finally, he wakes up only once every 4 years.

85
00:03:14,240 --> 00:03:18,620
To be compared to the Olympics, people call him the Olympic man.

86
00:03:19,580 --> 00:03:20,240
That's all.

87
00:03:21,660 --> 00:03:23,600
What? Higurashi was walking?

88
00:03:24,140 --> 00:03:26,280
But Higurashi must have been sleeping for 4 years.

89
00:03:27,840 --> 00:03:29,780
He woke up in the year of the Atlanta Olympics.

90
00:03:30,900 --> 00:03:32,640
The next one will be in 2000.

91
00:03:33,060 --> 00:03:33,260
Isn't it?

92
00:03:33,380 --> 00:03:34,500
Isn't it someone else's sky?

93
00:03:35,500 --> 00:03:36,640
No, it's not.

94
00:03:36,780 --> 00:03:40,360
I doubted for a moment, but there's no doubt about it.

95
00:03:40,800 --> 00:03:43,620
He was wearing a business suit, but it was completely Higurashi.

96
00:03:44,240 --> 00:03:45,600
Higurashi doesn't wear a suit.

97
00:03:46,880 --> 00:03:48,220
And he was walking in Shinjuku.

98
00:03:49,340 --> 00:03:54,820
But Higurashi gets really bad mood when he wakes up outside the Olympic city and goes crazy.

99
00:03:55,640 --> 00:03:56,100
I see.

100
00:03:56,720 --> 00:03:58,800
He woke up between Seoul Goring and Barcelona Goring.

101
00:04:00,600 --> 00:04:02,100
He's more terrifying than the Daimajin.

102
00:04:02,100 --> 00:04:05,700
He can easily blow up one or two buildings.

103
00:04:07,100 --> 00:04:07,700
What?

104
00:04:07,920 --> 00:04:11,900
So far, there's no damage to his supernatural powers, but it'll be bad if it happens.

105
00:04:12,600 --> 00:04:14,500
Ryotsu, go and check Higurashi's room.

106
00:04:15,400 --> 00:04:16,000
Yes.

107
00:04:21,860 --> 00:04:25,900
Senpai, you just need to check whether he's sleeping or not, but you don't have to dress like this.

108
00:04:28,260 --> 00:04:31,080
You don't know because you've never woken him up.

109
00:04:31,080 --> 00:04:31,340
I know.

110
00:04:31,340 --> 00:04:33,740
