This is Kochikame's ending song.

120
00:04:57,220 --> 00:04:57,880
No way.

121
00:04:57,880 --> 00:05:04,100
The ending song he sang when he woke up was "Hofudiran's Smile", so he doesn't know the ending song now.

122
00:05:07,140 --> 00:05:08,660
The key is not locked.

123
00:05:09,120 --> 00:05:09,560
What?

124
00:05:11,940 --> 00:05:12,540
