150
00:06:16,820 --> 00:06:17,700
I remember.

151
00:06:17,760 --> 00:06:18,260
He was doing that construction.

152
00:06:19,000 --> 00:06:19,700
I remember.

153
00:06:20,000 --> 00:06:22,620
