175
00:07:08,080 --> 00:07:09,940
I think it was after the expansion of the road.

176
00:07:11,120 --> 00:07:12,560
Last summer, huh?

177
00:07:12,580 --> 00:07:13,260
Oh, no.

178
00:07:13,680 --> 00:07:16,280
All right, let's go to the garbage disposal center on Yume Island.

179
